Class FarmLot

java.lang.Object
main.FarmLot
public class FarmLot extends Object
This class contains the constructor and methods in managing a farm lot

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors
    Constructor
    Description
    FarmLot()
    Constructs a farm lot with the necessary information such as plow status, water count, fertilize count, wither status, harvest status, seed information, and farm lot/tile occupation status.
